# Course Philosophy

This course integrates:

- Visual storytelling  
- Active learning  
- Live coding  
- Ethical analysis  
- Real-world AI systems  

Students finish the trimester having built, deployed, and audited real AI systems.

---

# Final Message

The future of AI belongs to engineers who combine:

- Technical depth  
- Deployment skills  
- Ethical responsibility  

Build responsibly. Deploy thoughtfully. Innovate ethically.

